OL,3,CPeople invited to line street ahead of
OL,4,CBonnie Tyler's funeral
OL,6,FPeople have been invited to line the
OL,7,Fstreet for a "celebration" of the life
OL,8,Fof iconic Welsh singer Bonnie Tyler.
OL,10,FThe Holding Out for a Hero artist,
OL,11,Fbirth name Gaynor, died on 8 July in
OL,12,FPortugal after previously having
OL,13,Femergency intestinal surgery in May.
OL,15,FHer family confirmed in a statement
OL,16,Fthat she had "unexpectedly passed
OL,17,Faway...as a result of the illness that
OL,18,Fshe was being treated for".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
