OL,3,CPeople invited to line street ahead of
OL,4,CBonnie Tyler's funeral
OL,6,FAccording to a funeral notice
OL,7,Fpublished in the South Wales Evening
OL,8,FPost and on the Funeral Notices
OL,9,Fwebsite, Tyler's funeral will be held
OL,10,Fon Monday 17 August after a
OL,11,Fcelebration of her live at Swansea
OL,12,FMinister that same day.
OL,14,FHowever on Saturday 15, people are
OL,15,Finvited to line Newtown Road in
OL,16,FMumbles as she is moved from the
OL,17,Ffuneral home.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
