OL,3,CPeople invited to line street ahead of
OL,4,CBonnie Tyler's funeral
OL,6,FA notice from William Pressdee
OL,7,FFuneralcare read: "Resting at William
OL,8,FPressdee Funeralcare, Mumbles until
OL,9,Fshe returns to her home, Fernhill, on
OL,10,FSaturday 15th August at 3.30pm - those
OL,11,Fwho wish to pay their respects are
OL,12,Finvited to line Newton Road, Mumbles
OL,13,Ffrom 3.15pm.
OL,15,F"A Celebration of Gaynor's life will
OL,16,Fbe held at Swansea Minster (St. Mary's
OL,17,FChurch) on Monday 17th August at
OL,18,F12noon.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
