PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784823525
OL,3,CPeople invited to line street ahead of
OL,4,CBonnie Tyler's funeral
OL,6,F"Gaynor will then return to her
OL,7,F'hometown', and travel through Skewen
OL,8,Fat approximately 1.20pm en route to a
OL,9,Fprivate family service of committal
OL,10,Fand farewell."
OL,12,FTyler's family has asked for donations
OL,13,Fto either Noah's Ark Children's
OL,14,FHospital for Wales or to Cerebral
OL,15,FPalsy Cymru, rather than flowers.
OL,17,FThe notice also says: "She is
OL,18,Fremembered as a warm, generous artist
OL,19,Fwhose music touched generations and
OL,20,Fcontinues to fill dance floors and
OL,21,Fkaraoke booths around the world.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
