PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784823525
OL,3,CPeople invited to line street ahead of
OL,4,CBonnie Tyler's funeral
OL,6,F"Her legacy lives on in the timeless
OL,7,Fsongs that made her a legend."
OL,9,FTyler was 75 when she died. She
OL,10,Frocketed to international fame in the
OL,11,F1980s, with the release of her hit
OL,12,Fsingle Total Eclipse Of The Heart
OL,13,Fwhich shot to the top of the charts in
OL,14,Fthe UK and US.
OL,16,FThe Grammy-nominated star was also due
OL,17,Fto tour Europe later this year to mark
OL,18,F50 years since the release of her 1976
OL,19,Fbreakthrough hit, Lost In France,
OL,20,Fwhich entered the charts across Europe.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
