OL,3,CPeople invited to line street ahead of
OL,4,CBonnie Tyler's funeral
OL,6,FShe was made an MBE in 2023 for her
OL,7,Fservices to music, after being named
OL,8,Fin the Queen's Birthday Honours list.
OL,10,FFollowing the acclaimed singer's
OL,11,Fdeath, tributes poured in from the
OL,12,Flikes of Sir Rod Stewart, Spandau
OL,13,FBallet frontman Tony Hadley and Sir
OL,14,FKeir Starmer.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
